         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Newyears eve 1881 ¶  ¶ I rejoyce with you, dear Sir Joseph, that Mr Bentham is spared us, ¶  and I trust that my prediction of his living into the next century will be fulfilled, though I shall not li...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.12.31a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Joseph Hooker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew correspondence, Australia, Mueller 1871-81, f. 348.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Newyears eve 1881</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I rejoyce with you, dear Sir Joseph, that Mr Bentham is spared us,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See J Hooker to M, 9 November 1881.</p>
               </note> and I trust that my prediction of his living into the next century will be fulfilled, though I shall not live to see the end of his great labors. I look forward to his genera of grasses with deep interest, and feel sure they will be kept by him in a conservative spirit.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham (1882), reported in J. Hooker to M, 9 November 1881, as having been read to the Linnean Society.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You and he will have some work yet, to bring up the arrear of genera of the last 20 years connectedly as a supplement. I still hope, that a volume in conformity will be issued on the Mosses, lichens, fungs &amp; algs.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My census of Australian genera with chronologic &amp; literary indication, including cryptogams, has gone now nearly through the press, the printer having received the finishing msc. some time ago.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B82.13.08.</p>
               </note> Unfortunately I shall not be able to profit from Mr Bentham's "gramineae" in time. A copy ought to be ready for you, complete, by next mail.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Though long post festum you will kindly accept my felicitation to the new year.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your friend General Sir John Lefroy honored me at my poor place with a call, so his Excellency<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Governor of Tasmania at this time.</p>
               </note> can describe to you how miserably I am situated here.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>From Dr Rudall, who just returned, I learnt to my regret, that he did not succeed to see you at the Medical Congress,<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>James Rudall attended the International Medical Congress, London, in August 1881.</p>
               </note> though he was able to present my letter of introduction to Dr Virchow there.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
